<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="121" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,583,646]" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">
This species was recorded for 
<collectingCountry box="[485,530,584,610]" name="Iran" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">Iran</collectingCountry>
based on erroneous determination of 
<bibRefCitation author="Medvedev, G. S." box="[946,1149,583,610]" pageId="16" pageNumber="121" refId="ref11059" refString="Medvedev, G. S. (1968) Fauna of the USSR. Coleoptera. Vol. 19. Issue. 2. Darkling beetles (Tenebrionidae). Subfamily Opatrinae. Tribes Platynotini, Dendarini, Pedinini, Dissonomini, Pachypterini, Opatrini (part) and Heterotarsini. Nauka, Leningrad, 285 pp. [in Russian]" type="book" year="1968">Medvedev (1968)</bibRefCitation>
. In fact, it occurs in 
<collectingCountry box="[1370,1432,583,609]" name="Syria" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">Syria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[151,196,620,646]" name="Iraq" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">Iraq</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[250,332,619,645]" name="Turkey" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">Turkey</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
